beer_brewer_name: Grumpy Troll Brewery, Restaurant and Pizzeria
review_blob: On draught at the brewery.  For the hop lover to be sure.  Aroma of pine and grapefruit, pours a nice amber color with ample head that dissipates quickly.  Fairly viscous mouth feel.  Wearing on the palate, but a very nice offering.

On draft at the Fantail Brewery, this is one delicious monster.  The aroma of grapefruit is overwhelming and the alcohol is, in my opinion, pretty well disguised.  Beautiful color and great head retention.  Next to a fresh Dreadnaught, this beer is my favorite.
